(948, 'Aripiprazole 30mg 20 f.c tab', 'اريبيبرازول 30 مجم 20 قرص', '114', '152', 'Aripiprazole', 'El- Obour', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'حالات الامراض النفسية -- علاج الاكتئاب -- علاج الانفصام الشخصية -- يؤخذ تحت اشراف طبي', 'Psychiatric antipsychotics', '30mg', 'Aripiprazole is indicated for the treatment of acute manic and mixed episodes associated with bipolar I disorder, irritability associated with autism spectrum disorder, schizophrenia, and Tourette''s disorder.[L45859] It is also used as an adjunctive treatment of major depressive disorder.[L45859 An injectable formulation of aripiprazole is indicated for agitation associated with schizophrenia or bipolar mania.[L45859] Finally, an extended-release, bimonthly injection formulation of aripiprazole is indicated for the treatment of adult schizophrenia and maintenance therapy for adult bipolar I disorder.[L46203]', '6224000866037', '', 4032, '2024-05-26', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
